UPSTREAM SOURCE
---------------
The dataset is derived from the 2024 Survey of Korean Artists, released
by the Korea Culture and Tourism Institute on behalf of the Ministry of
Culture, Sports and Tourism, Republic of Korea. The source statistical
report is made available under the Korea Open Government Licence Type 1
(KOGL Type 1), which permits redistribution and derivative works with
attribution and no prohibition on commercial use.

KOGL Type 1 terms: https://www.kogl.or.kr/info/license.do#01-tab

When citing the dataset, please also acknowledge the upstream source:
  Korea Culture and Tourism Institute. 2024 Survey of Korean Artists.
  Ministry of Culture, Sports and Tourism, Republic of Korea, 2024.

CC-BY-4.0 of this release is compatible with KOGL Type 1 attribution
requirements; both require attribution to the upstream rights holder
and impose no field-of-use restrictions.

---

PERSONAS ARE SYNTHETIC
----------------------
All personas in the dataset are synthetic. They were generated by a
language model conditioned on aggregate statistics from the upstream
source. No individual respondent record was used to generate any
persona. Resemblance to any real person is coincidental.
